item.title: jenna add a quote by Barbara Kingsolver
item.description: "Listen. To live is to be marked. To live is to change, to acquire the words of a story, and that is the only celebration we mortals really know. In perfect stillness, frankly, I've only found sorrow." -- Barbara Kingsolver

item.title: jenna add a quote by Jane Goodall

item.title: jenna add a quote by Sue Monk Kidd
item.description: "We are so limited, you have to use the same word for loving Rosaleen as you do for loving Coke with peanuts. Isn't that a shame we don't have many more ways to say it?" -- Sue Monk Kidd

item.title: jenna add a quote by Sue Monk Kidd
